---
const SITE_URL = "https://shows.undershows.com.br";
---
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Página não encontrada | Undershows</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta
      http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy"
      content="default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: https://media.undershows.com.br https://assets.undershows.com.br https://cms.undershows.com.br; connect-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'"
    />
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        color: #000;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #f05291, gray);
      }
      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 900px;
        padding: 24px 16px 48px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 160px;
        max-width: 50vw;
        margin: 0 auto 16px;
        display: block;
      }
      .box {
        max-width: 520px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
        border: 3px solid #000;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 16px;
      }
      h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 1.4rem; }
      p { margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700; }
      a { color: #000; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 800; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 3px solid #000;
        background: #ff4b92;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <a href="/">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="https://media.undershows.com.br/logo-undershows.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="https://media.undershows.com.br/logo-undershows.png" alt="Undershows" class="logo" />
        </picture>
      </a>

      <div class="box">
        <h1>No momento não temos shows cadastrados dessa banda.</h1>

        <p>
          Você pode enviar o cartaz por e-mail:
          <a href="mailto:undershowsbr@gmail.com">undershowsbr@gmail.com</a>
          ou pelo WhatsApp:
          <a href="https://wa.me/551152862298?text=Oi!%20Quero%20enviar%20um%20cartaz%20de%20show%20para%20a%20Undershows." target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            (11) 5286-2298
          </a>
        </p>

        <p>
          Aliás, se você curte vinil ou CD, dá uma olhadinha na nossa loja virtual:
          <a href="https://undershows.com.br" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            undershows.com.br
          </a>
        </p>

        <a class="btn" href={`${SITE_URL}/`}>← Voltar pros shows</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>